			      <para>
            <para.body>Given the sequence <math>
                  <latex>(a_n = 3n)</latex>
               </math>, find the first 5 elements of the tail end beginning with <math>
                  <latex>N=1,000,000</latex>
               </math>.</para.body>
         </para>
			      <math.display>
				        <latex>n\from \NNr \longrightarrow \NNr,\quad n(i):= i^2</latex>
